<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！咚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂用枕头捂住了耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么声音？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊翻过身来，看向天花板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！“是核桃。” 乔伊回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“核桃又开始掉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我要睡觉！” 凯蒂抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星期天的早上。” 乔伊小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她闭上了眼睛。突然，她又睁开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小提琴！” 她一边喊着一边掀起了被子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷和我今早要去找小提琴！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂用被子盖住了自己的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷和乔伊在阁楼找小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还找了仓库的柜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们找过大木箱子了吗？” 妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们找了妈妈和爸爸房间里的箱子，但还是没找到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，乔伊打开了走廊尽头的箱子盖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷拿出来一个旧相册，还有两张褪色的被子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这里！” 乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷从箱子里拿出黑盒子，打开了盖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 乔伊说。她摸着小提琴的老木头和断掉的琴弦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的小提琴。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这把小提琴演奏了很多音乐。” 爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷拿起一小块木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“琴桥弯了。” 爷爷说。他拿出了琴弓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像有什么东西没了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊指着琴弓两端乱乱的毛说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她充满期待地看着爷爷。“您觉得呢？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“旧小提琴能够重见天日应该很高兴。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，它需要修理一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天你去上学时，我会把它拿到贝兹市的音乐店去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看看能不能修好，用来演奏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，谢谢爷爷！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她张开双臂拥抱爷爷，用力地亲了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，乔伊焦急地等待着下课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>放学的铃声一响起，她就急忙冲到了自行车旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等我！” 凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，乔伊已经在路上飞驰了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当凯蒂到家时，乔伊已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈一个人坐在餐桌前，看着信件。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上的小提琴盒子开着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，我回来了。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把书包放到了地板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，宝贝。” 妈妈说，“这里有一封你的信哦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂的眼睛一亮。“信？给我的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你和乔伊的。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂撕开信封。“哦！这是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿着一张封面带有秋叶的卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“邀请函！” 她念道。她打开了卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坐干草车。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿杰生日那天会坐干草车，他邀请了我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂跑去厨房看日历。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是两个星期以后。我要告诉乔伊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在外面园子里和......” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，乔伊和爷爷从后门走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你猜怎么了！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，当她看见乔伊的脸时，她停住了。“你怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊有一个坏消息。” 妈妈对凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那把小提琴需要修理的地方很多，超出了我们的预想。” 爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“需要花100美元。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！” 凯蒂说，“现在该怎么办呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在修不起小提琴，” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着妈妈。“得等一等。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊深深地叹了一口气，关上了小提琴盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿起盒子上了楼。没有人说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，凯蒂想起了坐干草车的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等，乔伊！” 她喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个好消息！” 她追着乔伊上了楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>